-- Egan-Jones, Owner Sean Egan Accused of Misrepresentations by SEC
-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 2012-04-24T18:41:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-24/egan-jones-owner-sean-egan-accused-of-misrepresentations-by-sec.html
Egan-Jones Ratings Co. and the
firm’s owner and president,  Sean Egan , were sued by the U.S.
Securities and Exchange Commission, which  claimed  material
misrepresentations and omissions in the company’s July 2008
application to register as a ratings organization.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
